[01:49.04]	Behold our human actions, as they do,
[01:52.37]	I doubt not then but innocence shall make
[01:56.19]	False accusation blush and tyranny
[01:59.45]	Tremble at patience. You, my lord, best know,
[02:03.26]	Who least will seem to do so, my past life
